                           'HaffaChainy' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'HaffaChainy' is a Workbench @{"game" link play} where you have to rotate chainlinks
on a 6 by 8 tile board so they combine to make chains of 3 or more
chainlinks of the same colour, the more links there are in a chain, the
more points you get. Once a chain of 3 links or more is made, it is
removed from the board.

  As you progress in the game, bombs, unmoveable ('frozen') chainlinks,
blocks and 'siamese' tiles may appear on the game board.

  A Top 10 records the best scores and saves them on disk.

  Have fun!

